  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Digital Signage Solution",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Display Cast Lite (UC-Cast-Lite) is a streamlined digital signage player designed to deliver high-quality media content to any HDMI-compatible display. With support for media playback up to 1080p resolution, it ensures crisp and clear visuals for various applications, including advertising, informational displays, and interactive kiosks. The device connects effortlessly to displays via its HDMI port, transforming standard screens into dynamic digital signage platforms. Its compact dimensions of 90 x 52 x 31 mm (without mount) and lightweight design (160 g) allow for unobtrusive installation, making it suitable for a variety of environments."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Seamless Integration and Control",
      "text": "The Display Cast Lite integrates seamlessly with UniFi Connect (version 3.17.0 and later), allowing users to manage and schedule content remotely. This centralized management platform enables the creation of multimedia playlists and dynamic digital signage layouts, enhancing the versatility of the display content. The device also supports HDMI Consumer Electronics Control (CEC), allowing it to automatically power the connected display on or off, further simplifying operation and reducing energy consumption."
    }
  ],
